Setup for the test case presented in Goutiere et al.(2000) article.

For more details see "An assessment of real-gas modelling in 2D enclosures".
doi: https://doi.org/10.1016/S0022-4073(99)00102-8

Replace the functions present in RTS_functions.f90 with those present in user_functions.f90

To facilitate post-processing, replace these lines in the output.rts file.
!===============================================================
!                     Lineup Variable Save               
!===============================================================
.true.   !on/off lineup save module (only for 3D simulations)
 1        !Method: 1-Point 2-Node
 4        !Number of Lineups
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
! Axis  >>   X:(x,a,b)   Y:(a,y,b)   Z:(a,b,z)                  !
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
!             CV Point         CV Node      Variable            !
! Axis      a        b        a       b        ID               !
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
   x      0.25d0   0.00d0     10      10        3 
   y      0.50d0   0.00d0     10      10        3
   x      0.50d0   0.00d0     10      10        10
   y      1.00d0   0.00d0     10      10        10
!===============================================================
